# Production environment — Self-contained cPanel deployment
#
# ✅ NO Supabase connection in production
# ✅ Same build works on ANY domain automatically
# ✅ Each domain uses its own MySQL database (complete data isolation)
# ✅ API URL auto-detects from current domain: https://<domain>/api/api
# ✅ No VITE_API_URL needed — fully auto-detect
